d1-manager.description: D1 Manager is a web UI and API for Cloudflare D1, a serverless SQL database. It provides a user-friendly interface for managing databases, tables, and records, as well as an API for performing operations programmatically. D1 Manager simplifies database management, enabling users to focus on their data.
